thread.title: Deputies investigate Lacey shooting

author: kirotv.com
title: Deputies investigate Lacey shooting
text:
Authorities are investigating a shooting that left one dead and two injured Wednesday night in Lacey.
Authorities responded to multiple calls of gunshots in the 6100 block of Ruddell Road Southeast.
When deputies arrived, they found a deceased male.
Deputies said two people with gunshot wounds were at a nearby hospital. Authorities suspect the two are involved.
Authorities will continue their investigation.
